<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-fear-of-sth">in fear (of sth)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>恐惧(某事)；担心 (某事)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If someone comes up behind you and touches you lightly on the shoulder, you may jump in fear.
如果有人从身后走近你，并轻触你的肩膀，你可能会吓一跳。</p><footer>2010 陕西</footer></div></div>